@startuml Cross-Platform Experience
title Cross-Platform Experience

actor "Mobile User" as MobileUser
participant "Mobile Client" as Mobile
actor "Web User" as WebUser
participant "Web Client" as Web
participant "Web API" as API
participant "PostgreSQL DB" as DB

' Cross-Platform Experience Flow
MobileUser -> Mobile: Browse feed
activate Mobile
Mobile -> API: GET /feed
activate API
API -> DB: Query posts\n(include mobile params)
activate DB
DB --> API: Post data
deactivate DB
API --> Mobile: Standardized JSON response
deactivate API
Mobile --> MobileUser: Display unified UI
deactivate Mobile

WebUser -> Web: Browse feed
activate Web
Web -> API: GET /feed
activate API
API -> DB: Query posts\n(include web params)
activate DB
DB --> API: Same post data
deactivate DB
API --> Web: Same standardized JSON
deactivate API
Web --> WebUser: Display unified UI
deactivate Web

note over API #LightBlue
**Feature Parity Enforcement**:
1. Single API version for all clients
2. Response standardization middleware
3. Platform-specific parameters handled in business logic
end note
@enduml